    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve truly babied it since day one. It looks and drives just like it did when it first rolled off the lot, with not a single detail overlooked. If you've been looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look. \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
