      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It is in absolutely stunning, showroom-ready condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve meticulously cared for every inch of this car, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for perfection, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have!",
